{
  "stem": "11611.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was about a 200-page report on the marvels that the Dresdner Bank had accomplished in taking over Jewish properties, to the extent of two, three billion Reichsmarks.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Primarily within Germany, but in Czechoslovakia heavily and elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very proud of this and somebody prepared a book on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All in one place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't find it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was delivered to me by someone who did find it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had investigators and interpreters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a-- my primary reliance was a guy named Otto [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Verber ?] who was an Austrian Jew who had left Vienna somewhere around 1938 and served with distinction in the American army as an intelligence officer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was damn good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He knew Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He knew Austria.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He knew the politics and he-- obviously he was very good in Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a-- German was his native language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was like a chemistry undergraduate, I think, in one of the German or Austrian universities from Vienna before he left the country, when the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Must have been '38.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he turned up a lot of this stuff and did a lot of the translation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was fairly acute.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'll get further into his background later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Anyhow, somewhere towards the end of '47 or maybe the beginning of '48, Taylor called all of us into his office and said that the trials were going to be curtailed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were out of step with the whole occupation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were busy prosecuting Germans at a time when official policy was to secure the Germans for our side in the Cold War.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Russians were, of course, doing the same thing in their areas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And therefore, we were really out of step.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
